data.description: Massive price improvement on this beautiful Cabin in Big Bear's hidden gem of Sugarloaf. ALL FURNISHINGS & DECOR ARE INCLUDED. This is the vacation home dreams are made of, a quiet mountain retreat with groceries, shopping, and the entertainment of Big Bear Lake and the SLOPES only 10 minutes away. This large three bedroom, two bath modern gambrel cabin sits on a double lot that is slightly elevated from the freshly-paved street, and offers beautiful sunset and forest views from the expansive wrap-around deck. The property welcomes you in to an entryway with space for all your snowboards or skis and a large coat closet. Step upstairs into an abundance of natural light from the large updated windows and gorgeous high ceilings. The recently-remodeled kitchen boasts brand-new stainless steel appliances, new countertops, and the entire cabin has been freshly painted. The updated light fixtures maintain the modern rustic feel of the property. The open-air primary bedroom in the large loft enjoys the best views of beautiful mountains and tree tops. MUST SEE TO APPRECIATE!    The new happy owners or short term rental guests will experience utmost privacy with a single bedroom on each level and plenty of space for a crowd. You can sleep 13 guests of your own if you utilized the trundle and pull out couches ALL INCLUDED WITH THE SALE! The convenient shuttle stop at the local general store easily brings you to Big Bear Mountain, Snow Summit Ski Resort, Oktoberfest, or to the nightlife and dining in the village. The paved driveway features 4 parking spaces for your family and guests. Included with the furnishings and decor is a fully stocked kitchen with newer toaster, airfryer, coffee maker, crockpot and anything else you need to begin building your own cozy cabin memories. Smart home devices like a nest thermostat and ring security camera also are included with the sale. The yard is fully fenced in for your furry friends and the wrap around deck features comfortable lounge furniture, a Tree Hammock and a porch swing perfect for taking in sunset views and epic starry nights.
